Why String is immutable in java?

	string is immutable in java becuase of the security perpose. suppose if string is mutable in java 
	then and if someone made changes in the string then it will be applied to everywhere and some important imformation 
	get disturbed. so that is a reason to keep string is immutable.
	

what is the difference between String and String Builder?	

	String									String Builder
------------------------------------------------------------------	
string is immutable					String Builder helps to do change in
									string by creating modified string with
									the help of different methods.	
---------------------------------------------------------------------------

									